item.title: Lakerbotics 2020 Code
item.description: Description Lakerbotics-1649’s robot code, written in java. This code was created from base to suit our robot’s needs and the challenge’s (Infinite Recharge) demands. Months of testing and research was spent learning the libraries required, and the “final version” of the robot code was developed over nearly 2 months. I have written the majority of this code (under the Lakerbotics Github account), and the overall project was a group effort with 2 other team members.
